{"lastModified":1748869985409,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::a7a8c530-3a47-11f0-956e-99e344c602dc","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nCruising in Perfect Serenity\n\nIn keeping with the spirit of the line, the Sun Odyssey 440 is a cruising sailboat designed for off-shore sailing. Its resistance, stability, and secure cockpit make it a faithful companion on longer crossings. Careful attention has been paid to fit and finish and to the level of comfort on board – with integrated ventilation, sound insulation, a well-equipped galley, careful selection of materi-als, an exterior sundeck, etc. – to create living spaces dedicated to the enjoyment of life’s simple pleasures and the voyage, itself.\n\nA Sailboat in Your Image\n\nThe Sun Odyssey 440 offers multiple interior layouts: from the version with two immense cabins and a storage locker, to the version with four cabins, able to accommodate up to 10 people, with two in the saloon. For those adept at gentle, perfect manoeuvres, a bow thruster is available. An optional high-performance mast is available to satisfy lovers of speed and performance. And for long-distance sailors, it is possible to integrate a water-maker, solar panels, and additional batteries. Numerous options enable you to configure your boat in function with your needs and preferences.","blueprint":{"name":"NIMERTIS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::a7a8c530-3a47-11f0-956e-99e344c602dc::assets::afde9930-3a49-11f0-a760-ab898bf48f00/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::a7a8c530-3a47-11f0-956e-99e344c602dc::assets::afdbb300-3a49-11f0-a760-ab898bf48f00/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::a7a8c530-3a47-11f0-956e-99e344c602dc::assets::afef6210-3a49-11f0-a760-ab898bf48f00/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::a7a8c530-3a47-11f0-956e-99e344c602dc::assets::afecf110-3a49-11f0-a760-ab898bf48f00/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::a7a8c530-3a47-11f0-956e-99e344c602dc::assets::afe